text: Marianela Robinet (born 24 November 1983) is an Argentine volleyball player. She played at the 2002 FIVB Volleyball Women's World Championship. 2005 Women's Pan-American Volleyball Cup, 2008 Women's Pan-American Volleyball Cup, 2009 Women's South American Volleyball Championship, 009 Women's Pan-American Volleyball Cup, 2010 Women's Pan-American Volleyball Cup. She played for Central San Carlos. == References == Category:Argentine volleyball players Category:Living people Category:1983 births
